name: us-prosecutor-database-data
description: The United States Prosecutor Database (Data) is a dataset collection of elected and appointed government attorneys in the United States (including Attorney Generals, U.S. Attorneys, District/State Attorneys, and Municipal/County/City Attorneys). It aims to showcases prosecutorial demographics, culture, and history at the local, state, and federal level.
author: Billimarie Lubiano Robinson <work@billimarie.com>
